）全球0800【全球疫情汇总】据新浪实时统计，截至3月10日8点，除中国（包括港澳台地区）以外，海外新冠肺炎累计确诊30585例，死亡764例，治愈3774例。
As of 8: 00 on March 10, a total of 30,585 new cases of pneumonia (including Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan) had been diagnosed, 764 deaths and 3,774 cases cured, according to Sina Real-Time Statistics.
数据来源：新浪0800【世卫组织：全球性大流行的威胁“非常真实”】世界卫生组织总干事谭德塞9日说，新冠肺炎疫情已在许多国家出现，该疫情构成大流行的威胁“已经变得非常真实。
Data source: Sina 0800 [WHO: The Threat of a Global Pandemic is "very real") World Health Organization Director General Theresa Tupper said Wednesday that the outbreak of New Crown Pneumonia has emerged in many countries and the threat of a pandemic has become very real.
”但他说，虽然形势严峻，新冠肺炎疫情将是“历史上第一次可以控制的大流行。
But despite the severity of the situation, he said, the outbreak would be "the first time in history that a controllable pandemic can be brought under control."
”0800【WHO：全球累计确诊新冠肺炎病例超11万，除中国外韩国最多】世界卫生组织（WHO）官员9日表示，随着新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情在全球范围的迅速蔓延，出现全球性流行病的威胁正在上升。
The threat of a global epidemic is on the rise as the global outbreak of the new coronavirus pneumonia spreads rapidly, officials from the World Health Organization (WHO) said Wednesday.
报告称，尽管新冠肺炎疫情在中国的蔓延速度正在放缓，但在世界其他地区正在加速扩散，并已传播到100多个国家，全球累计确诊病例逾11.1万。
Although the spread of the outbreak in China is slowing, it is accelerating in other parts of the world and has spread to more than 100 countries, with a cumulative global total of more than 111,000 cases, the report said.
0800【欧洲理事会采取预防措施，防止新冠肺炎疫情在欧扩散】欧洲理事会9日发表公告称，鉴于新冠肺炎疫情在欧洲扩散，欧洲理事会决定采取一系列预防措施：一、减少理事会会议、准备会和工作会数量；二、减少参加理事会的各个代表团人数；三、所有的访问和非核心培训将取消；四、鼓励理事会员工尽量减少内部会议。
The European Council decided to take a series of preventive measures in view of the spread of the outbreak in Europe. First, reduce the number of Council meetings, preparatory meetings and working sessions; secondly, reduce the number of delegations to the Council; thirdly, all visits and non-core training will be cancelled; and fourthly, encourage Council staff to minimize internal meetings.
意大利0800【意大利总理宣布对全国采取封闭措施】据CNN消息，当地时间9日晚，意大利总理孔特表示，为遏制新冠肺炎疫情蔓延，从2月10日上午开始，对北部伦巴第大区采取的封闭措施扩展至全国，意大利各地学校的停课时间延长至4月3日。
LONDON (Reuters) - The closure of the northern region of Lombardy has been extended nationwide since the morning of February 10 to curb the spread of the new crown pneumonia, with schools across Italy suspended until April 3, Italian Prime Minister Gianfranco Conte said, according to CNN.
目前“整个意大利现在都处于封闭状态”。
"The whole of Italy is now closed," he said.
