Iran cancels New Year's Message Iran's Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei will cancel his New Year's message because of the outbreak of pneumonia, Iranian Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei will cancel his New Year's message to avoid gathering and increase the risk of spreading the virus, Iran's Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei said Monday.
通常，在伊朗诺鲁孜新年第一天（3月20日），伊朗最高领袖将发表新年致辞，这也被认为是每年最重要的讲话之一。
Iran's top leader is expected to deliver a New Year's address on the first day of the Iranian New Year's Day, which is also considered one of the most important speeches of the year.
0800【伊朗累计确诊7161例新冠肺炎病例，死亡237例】法国0800【法国新冠肺炎确诊病例增至1412例，死亡25例】法国的确诊病例数继续呈现快速上升趋势。
0800 [Iran] Cumulatively 7,161 new cases of crowns pneumonia and 237 deaths French confirmed cases of pneumonia have increased to 1,412 and the number of confirmed cases in France continues to show a rapid upward trend.
法国卫生总署署长萨洛蒙在当晚的记者会上说，法国9日确诊病例数为286例，出现新的聚集性感染。
At a news conference that evening, French Health Minister Philippe Salomon said there were 286 confirmed cases and new cases of conglomerate infection.
他透露，重症病例已经增至66例，这些患者都在重症监护室接受治疗。
He says the number of serious cases has increased to 66, all of whom are being treated in intensive care units.
0800【法国文化部长感染新冠病毒】法国文化部长雷斯特被感染的消息备受各界关注。
French Culture Minister Jean-Claude Roest has drawn attention to the news that he has been infected.
他是9日接受新型冠状病毒测试时被确认为阳性的。
He was confirmed to be positive when he was tested for the new coronavirus on the 9th.
雷斯特近期还曾与法国总统马克龙及多名法国部长级高官一起开会，并曾参加多项文化活动。
Lester also recently held meetings with French President Marc Ronny and a number of high-level French ministerial officials and participated in a number of cultural events.
法国媒体的初步分析认为，雷斯特是上周参加法国国民议会(议会下院)会议时，与国民议会中的确诊患者接触而被感染的。
Preliminary analysis by the French media suggests that Lester was infected last week during a meeting of the French National Assembly (lower house of parliament) with confirmed patients in the National Assembly.
现在法国国民议会已有多名议员和工作人员被确诊，其中一名议员病情严重。
Several members of the French National Assembly and its staff have now been diagnosed, one of whom is seriously ill.
0800【法国巴黎机场集团总裁确诊感染新冠肺炎】美国0800【美股熔断！开盘全线暴跌超7%，三大股指暂停交易15分钟】3月9日晚间，美股三大指数开盘全线重挫。
Paris airport group president confirmed the outbreak of new crown pneumonia U.S. shares fell more than 7% across the board, trading was suspended for 15 minutes March 9 The three main indexes fell sharply in the evening of March 9.
标普500指数跌7%，触发熔断机制，美股三大股指全部暂停交易15分钟。
The S & P 500 fell 7%, triggering a meltdown that suspended trading in all three U. S. stock indexes for 15 minutes.
截至当天收盘，道琼斯工业平均指数下跌2013.76点，收于23851.02点，跌幅为7.79%。
By the end of the day, the Dow Jones Industrial Average was down 2013.76 points, or 7.79%, to 23851.02.
标准普尔500种股票指数下跌225.81点，收于2746.56点，跌幅为7.60%。
The Standard & Poor's 500-stock index fell 225.81 points, or 7.60%, to 2,746.56.
纳斯达克综合指数下跌624.94点，收于7950.68点，跌幅为7.29%。
The Nasdaq Composite Index fell 624.94 points, or 7.29 per cent, to 7950.68.
美国10年期国债收益率再次突破历史新低降至0.5%以下，30年期美国国债收益率也首次跌破1%。
Yields on US 10-year Treasury bonds have again fallen below all-time lows of 0.5 per cent, and 30-year Treasury yields have fallen below 1 per cent for the first time.
0800【美国确诊病例增至687，美国多所大学升级应对措施】据CNN统计，截至美东时间9日傍晚，全美已确诊至少687例新冠肺炎病例，其中包括死亡病例22例。
At least 687 cases of new crown pneumonia, including 22 deaths, have been confirmed nationwide by the evening of Tuesday, according to CNN.
疫情迅速蔓延至全美34个州和首都华盛顿特区，至少10个州宣布进入紧急状态。
The epidemic quickly spread to 34 states and Washington, D.C., and at least 10 states declared a state of emergency.
哥伦比亚大学、普林斯顿大学、加州大学伯克利分校、纽约大学、斯坦福大学等均采取了暂时停课转而线上授课的措施。
Columbia University, Princeton University, University of California, Berkeley, New York University, Stanford University and others have taken steps to suspend classes and switch to online classes.
西班牙0800【西班牙新冠肺炎确诊病例增至1223例】据西班牙《国家报》消息，据西班牙卫生部及各大自治区发布数据，西班牙新冠肺炎确诊病例增至1223例，其中死亡28例，治愈30例。
Spain's new crown pneumonia has risen to 1,223 confirmed cases, including 28 deaths and 30 cures, according to Spain's Ministry of Health and the Autonomous Communities, according to the Spanish newspaper El Pais.
此前据西班牙卫生部9日发布的最新数据，截至当天18时，西班牙新冠肺炎确诊病例累计已达1204例。
The total number of confirmed cases of pneumonia in Spain had reached 1204 by 1800 hours, according to the latest figures released on Monday by the Spanish Health Ministry.
塞浦路斯0800【塞浦路斯首次确诊新冠肺炎病例】塞浦路斯卫生部长约安努9日说，已确诊的两例病例均为输入型病例。
Cyprus 0800 [Cyprus first confirmed cases of pneumonia] Cyprus Health Minister Joanu 9 said the two confirmed cases are imported cases.
约安努在当晚举行的新闻发布会上说，其中一例为日前从英国回国的64岁医务人员，另一例为从意大利旅行回国的25岁男子。
One is a 64-year-old medical worker who has returned from Britain, and the other is a 25-year-old man who returned from Italy, Joanou said at a news conference.
至此，欧盟27国在新冠面前已“无一幸免”。
So far, the EU's 27 countries have been "spared" from the new crown.
布基纳法索0800【布基纳法索首次确诊两例新冠肺炎病例】布基纳法索卫生部长克劳丁·卢热9日晚召开新闻发布会说，该国首次确诊两例新冠肺炎病例。
Burkinabé 0800 [Burkina Faso first confirmed two cases of pneumonia] Burkina Faso's health minister, Claudien Luge, said in a news conference Tuesday night that the country had first confirmed two cases of new crown pneumonia.
卢热说，两人是一对夫妇，妻子最近有法国旅行史。
Luge said the couple were married and that their wife had a recent French travel history.
英国0800【英国新冠肺炎确诊病例增至280例，累计死亡3例】9日，英国政府紧急委员会召开了“眼镜蛇会议”，以决定是否采取措施来延缓新冠病毒在英国的传播。
Britain's emergency committee convened a meeting of cobras to decide whether to take steps to slow the spread of the new crown jewels in Britain.
这些措施包括禁止举办大型活动，关闭学校，鼓励人们在家工作等。
Such measures included banning large-scale events, closing schools and encouraging people to work from home.
瑞典0800【瑞典央行副行长新冠病毒检测结果呈阳性】俄罗斯0800【俄罗斯新冠肺炎确诊病例又增加3例，累计20例】据俄新社3月9日援引俄罗斯新冠疫情防控指挥部通告，当天在俄罗斯境内又确诊了3例新冠病毒感染病例，患者均居住在莫斯科。
RUSSIAN FEDERATION (Reuters) - Russia has confirmed three new cases of Crested Pneumonia, with three new cases confirmed in Russia on Monday, the central bank said, citing a report from Russia's New Crown Disease Control and Prevention Command.
到目前为止，俄罗斯确诊新冠病例总数已达20例。
So far, a total of 20 new cases have been confirmed in Russia.
以色列0800【以色列新冠肺炎确诊增至50例，航空公司取消所有国际航班】当地时间3月9日深夜（北京时间3月10日清晨），以色列航空公司突然宣布：由于新冠肺炎在以色列有蔓延趋势，以色列航空取消所有国际航班。
Israeli Airlines canceled all international flights in the early morning hours of March 9 (10: 00 a.m. Beijing time) as Israel Airlines cancelled all international flights because of the spread of New Crown Pneumonia in Israel.
据以色列电视台第13频道报道，以色列航空公司Arkia和Israir都将取消所有国际航班。
According to Israeli television channel 13, both Israeli airlines Arkia and Israel will cancel all international flights.
Arkia将立即停飞所有国际航班，Israir将从下周开始取消国际航班，直到5月为止。
Arkia will suspend all international flights immediately, and Israel will cancel international flights from next week until May.
0800【内塔尼亚胡宣布，任何进入以色列的外籍人士需隔离14天】荷兰0800【荷兰新增56例新冠肺炎确诊病例，累计321例】埃及0800【埃及暂停所有大型集会，以防新冠病毒传播】据埃及当地媒体9日报道，埃及总理穆斯塔法·马德布利决定暂停所有具有大型民众聚集性质的活动，其中包括一切埃及境内各省间的包含民众流动的大规模集会活动，集会活动恢复时间将另行通知。
0800 [Egypt suspends all large gatherings to prevent the spread of the virus) Egyptian Prime Minister Mustafa al-Maburi has suspended all mass gatherings, including all mass gatherings involving the movement of people between Egyptian governorates until further notice.
此举是埃及政府为应对新冠病毒蔓延所采取的预防措施的一部分， 有关部门将负责执行这项决定。
The move is part of the Egyptian government's preventive response to the spread of the new crown virus, and the authorities will be responsible for its implementation.
印度0800【印度新冠肺炎确诊病例增至43例】德国0800【德国9日报告两例新冠肺炎死亡病例，这是德国本土自疫情暴发以来首次报告死亡病例】加拿大0800【加拿大出现首例新冠肺炎死亡病例】加拿大不列颠哥伦比亚省医疗官波尼⋅亨利当地时间9日上午举行新闻发布会确认，该省一位男性老年人在感染新冠病毒之后于8日夜里在当地一家医院去世。
Germany reported two deaths from Newcrown Pneumonia Wednesday, the first reported deaths in mainland Germany. Canada's first case of Newly Coronary Pneumonia was reported in Canada.
这是加拿大境内发生新冠病毒疫情以来，第一个死于与新冠病毒感染有关的患者。
It was the first person to die from a New Crown virus infection in Canada.
